The anti-Hugenberg forces within the party have all left in separate ways. Committed <span style="color: #3E88B3;">nationalists</span> form a new <i>Konservative Volkspartei</i> (Conservative People's Party), while more pragmatic members and trade unionists choose to join the <span style="color: #000000;">Center Party</span>. It is a question of how long this party would last, since it finds itself in the small political base to the right of the <span style="color: #000000;">Center</span>, but to the left of the <span style="color: #3E88B3;">**DNVP**</span>.